name: Alice Wanmi
description: I am easy going lady and God fearing. i like to relax, eat good food, have drinks, hang out at the beach and pool. My personal time is mostly spent relaxing, dining out, drinks, cooking at home. I like to hang out in the sun, beach, pool, hot tub, eat in nice restaurants with an immense amount of conversation, jokes and laughter then it would work out nicely. If you like to bungee jump. I like writing and reading. I love giving surprises and never forget an occasion. I hate celebrating things the traditional way. I love to travel. I also love to keep fit and do yoga and go to gym .
